<div class="content">
    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Choose High-Paying Programs</h2>
        <p>Focus on affiliate networks like Amazon Associates, ClickBank, and high-ticket AI software platforms.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. Review Products You Use</h2>
        <p>Write simple reviews about tools you use—construction gear, power tools, apps, or gadgets.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Share Tutorials or Tips</h2>
        <p>Create short posts, TikToks, or videos showing “how to do ___” and include affiliate links.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Build a Simple Website</h2>
        <p>This very site you’re building can act as your affiliate hub for passive income.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. Track Your Earnings</h2>
        <p>Use Google Analytics or built-in dashboards to see what’s earning and increase those efforts.</p>
    </div>
